<l>nāṇoṭu nallāṇmai paṇṭuṭaiyē ṉiṉṟuṭaiyēṉ </l>
<l>kāmuṟṟā rēṟum maṭal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Modesty and manliness were once my own; now, my own is the palmyra horse that is ridden by the lustful.</l>
            </lg>
